{"tid":1021870,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［又一年特備節目］又係我去bbq喇","createTime":"2019-02-14T14:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T03:06:48.000Z","uid":34889,"like":29,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6c95611d41ef155c4a2111c65dd2f2bb01c97aa0","tid":1021870,"uid":34889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:16:40.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人記得上年情人節有條毒撚自己去咗石澳bbq同埋睇唔到日出呢？<br />\n<br />\n今年又係我呀，不過今年冇去遠行，<br />\n亦都唔睇日出，因為聽日要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於點解會開旅遊台呢？<br />\n係因為上年都係呢度見大家呀，<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，照舊去圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PX6newU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPX6newU.png&h=1bdd2117&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CvhxBLh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCvhxBLh.png&h=c4b2f875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多謝上年陪我嘅巴絲，<br />\n我想講承咗你地嘅貴言，我今年真係唔使自己燒了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJJpsR2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJJpsR2.png&h=55a03da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢仲話要每年情人節都去bbq，<br />\n諗咗一陣開唔開呢個po好，<br />\n不過我想話畀大家聽我多謝上年祝福我嘅大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e30380026f9936e7c859dbe39d13bf3c021b1e4","tid":1021870,"uid":25857,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:20:46.000Z","msg":"叻啦叻啦威啦威啦 今年唔洗一個人啦"},{"pid":"6ceb8603eeb39ce128c6daaa15fd1dc438675fd3","tid":1021870,"uid":13381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:22:36.000Z","msg":"威啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望你年年都有女朋友過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3410895fe4ecea02e9820556f480460302f0e5b3","tid":1021870,"uid":34889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ceb8603eeb39ce128c6daaa15fd1dc438675fd3","tid":1021870,"uid":13381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,